                                        {
                                            "name":  "Stinkbrain",
                                            "description":  "Throw a mushroom that periodically sheds poisonous spores, inflicting \u003cDT_VIRAL_COLOR\u003e Viral Damage and Status Effect upon nearby enemies while also lulling them to sleep.",
